project: The most common enemy is the mushroom. He can be killed by jumping on his head.
Birds can also be killed by jumping on the head. But be careful because these enemies will also fly every few seconds!
The prickly ones are the most dangerous and, in fact, invincible enemies and cannot be killed in any way. So you just have to jump over them and avoid hitting them.
Use the touch on the screen to jump or use the up arrow key or the W key to jump.
